original_title: ROH: Death Before Dishonor X - State of Emergency
overview: Death Before Dishonor X: State of Emergency (DBD X) was the tenth Death Before Dishonor professional wrestling internet pay-per-view (iPPV) event produced by Ring of Honor (ROH). It took place on September 15, 2012, at the Frontier Fieldhouse in Chicago Ridge, Illinois.
title: ROH: Death Before Dishonor X - State of Emergency
